  "title": "Admin Assistant (East, Healthcare) #HRY",
  "description": "<p>📍Joy Connect (Near Lavendar MRT) - 6 months contract</p><p>📍Tampines Central - 6 months contract/perm</p><p></p><p>⏰Mon - Fri: Any 8.5hrs in between 730am - 6pm</p><p>No weekends</p><p></p><p>🍀Job scope</p><p>• Conduct admission of clients into the centre services, by ensuring proper explanation to the Next of Kin/Client of charges, subsidy, means test application, MOU signing and arranging of assessment/start date/transport.</p><p>• Carry out reception duties and registration of clients for attendance taking purpose.</p><p>• Answer phone calls and enquiries, coordination of meetings.</p><p>• Collect payment for clients’ invoices and to keep a good record of collection balance account</p><p>• Filing of document, monthly statistics/utilisations.</p><p>• Update client’s profile regularly to ensure important information (eg. HHMT) and related demographic is accurate in the system.</p><p>• Assist Centre Supervisor/Manager in tracking of admin and centre consumables utilization and to ensure replenishment of stock.</p><p>• Assist Centre Supervisor/Manager in managing the transport schedule and to work with Next of Kin/Client on the transport arrangement.</p><p>• Perform any other duties as assigned from time to time.<br /></p><p>Interested applicants, please email your updated CV to rachel.lim@recruitexpress.com.sg or WA 97527630 for more information.</p><p></p><p>We regret to inform that only shortlisted candidates will be contacted.</p><p></p><p>EA Personnel No: R23116144</p><p>EA Personnel Name: Lim Ruo Yi, Rachel</p><p>Company EA license No.: Recruit Express Pte Ltd (99C4599)</p>",
